Search for Venmo users

Usage: search [OPTIONS] <QUERY>

Arguments:
  <QUERY>
          Search text

Options:
      --limit <N>
          Server request page size

          [default: 10]

      --offset <N>
          Zero-based user-search offset

          [default: 0]

  -h, --help
          Print help
